Crunch - a wordlist generator.

crunch <min> <max> [charset] [options]


Realistic example : crunch 6 6 -t admin%
    admin0
    admin1
    admin2
    admin3
    .....

-o output.txx
-s [] | starting crunch
-e [] | Ending crunch
-p [] | permutations (abc = abc, acb, bac, bca, cab, cba)
-b [] | Splits by size
-c [] | Lines per file

Pattern [-t] @ = letter % = number
    Pattern@% -> Patternz1

